Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座堆滿了破銅爛鐵的城市 它的能量之源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日膨脹著慾望的城市 它的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}混蛋 裕二是我的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…這一帶最強的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前左右「東京災時記」的特輯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採訪池袋最強傳說時遇見的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人周圍的空氣起了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能這麼描述…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 讓我動用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 你以為你神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個性騷擾老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我這個靠在三流雜誌上寫寫緋聞度日的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取回了年輕時單純的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 強烈的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想瞭解最強男人的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於隨之而來的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報道延後了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道事件的詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市某處 魑魅魍魎蠢蠢欲動的魔都氣息越來越濃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶要有大事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最強的男人必也將與其有某種形式的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重新開始了池袋特輯的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定從他周圍收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吃蟹子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我沒有點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 靜雄的朋友就是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您下的單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這日語是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（與俄羅斯壽司店員塞蒙氏的談話）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在說什麼哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒見過他打架時的場景嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 打架不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平才好 看著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝王蚌好（同音）？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊帝王蚌一份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞蒙是和平主義者 怎麼能談打架的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在問他誰是這一帶最強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是問道上的專家比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（與目出井組系栗楠會幹部四木氏的談話）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說池袋最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…聽說您這邊對這種事比較瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在已經不是打架的時代了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幹的全是些腦力活而不是體力活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 很清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 當然一旦被人小瞧就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找上門打架的 就算他是個外行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他掏刀還是掏槍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會徹底打垮他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上鬧騰的人不是我們這些內行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨是些毛頭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼達拉斯 什麼黃巾賊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不妨礙到我們的買賣 我們也井水不犯河水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近似乎還有什麼無頭騎士 什麼斬人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像都市傳說一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 說到這一帶最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他打架光明磊落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰 還有個情報販子知道得比我們更多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 請務必介紹給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不說代價…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過記者小哥 關於我們的買賣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪打聽到我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（與新宿情報販子折原臨也的談話）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…唔…情報源其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 東京災時記對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介紹些離奇事件和團隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下期是池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都知道那就好說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實概念上想寫個決定池袋最強的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一帶的強人多得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒手打架要數壽司店的塞蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥都能用的話要數阿靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿 阿靜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你是來問他的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…是吧 那位靜雄先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的事情 只要我知道就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿他沒轍所以想瞭解他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就很不愉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能通融通融…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說贄川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令嬡還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那種事情轉學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當父親的很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前 接觸平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和路燈一起騰空的雜誌記者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那一帶四處打聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會影響我的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那一帶發生了很多騷動對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:08:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和達拉斯 黃巾賊之間的對抗有關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而導火索是斬人魔事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬人魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就有難以控制的都市傳說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想再添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要是想打聽平和島靜雄的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你介紹個他的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報販子折原氏 給我介紹了個意料之外的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個忠告對你有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸你別在阿靜面前談他弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你早半年告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒的事是飛來橫禍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個讀高二的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從妻子跟了別人後 我和她相依為命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我不認為女兒會敬重我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始變得只為錢寫報道 就是為了女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是快遞員塞爾堤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（與快遞員塞爾堤的談話）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄是我無話不談的好友 對我而言是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過惹他生氣還是很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我的計劃是找出這一帶打架最強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家雜誌很喜歡這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如飆車族排行榜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慚愧慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這一帶也有人說你是最強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 靜雄比我強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙強到令人感動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是打架或格鬥技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他是狼人或者魔人也毫無爭議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 外星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對小灰人有心理陰影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 格鬥技巧鍛煉得再好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被手槍打中就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 他的實力就像是手槍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}這比較本身無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親身體會到的平和島靜雄的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個都市傳說的人物竟會說得滔滔不絕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那是不同次元的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是腎上腺素在腦內起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才發揮出極限的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越人類極限的瞬間爆發力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可謂超乎常規
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我單純的好奇心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話…能不能給我看看頭盔下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…也不為難你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 塞爾堤氏一定是位魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復平靜後我又重新開始採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳到耳中的是達拉斯和黃巾賊抗爭的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「達拉斯決定徹底無視對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而黃巾賊的首領將軍或許會採取行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃巾賊的後輩們也不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}傳說只有高層人士才見過廬山真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴加叮囑黃巾賊成員別和折原臨也扯上關係的將軍的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…那個最強的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬人魔事件頻發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃巾賊似乎認為那是達拉斯干的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天前女高中生在這裡遇襲的事件裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說只有一個少女得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不經意間把她和自己的女兒重合到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親奮不顧身地保護遭到斬人魔襲擊的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在女兒是…我無法理解的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 今天一定要面對她 面對心愛的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天遭到斬人魔的冤大頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是那個在《東京Warrior》裡寫東京災時記報道的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雜誌記者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我騙過你們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞頓認識他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這本雜誌的粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 下次我也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望警察多加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——罪歌進入聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想砍人咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還 不行…強者 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪歌 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 塞頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不理我們的回帖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須…砍更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍了人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是斬人魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你認識靜雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}愛 靜雄 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}愛…靜雄 愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}我要砍了平和島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}砍了 我愛平和島 愛 砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}平和島 靜雄 砍 愛 平和島 砍 砍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}愛靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}母親的希望 平和島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}母親的希望 靜雄 母親的希望 愛 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}平和島 母親的希望 砍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}愛 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}砍 我愛平和島…砍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}我要砍平和島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}愛 靜雄 母親的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}母親的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs34}{\fad(0,300)}靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——罪歌退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏裡 多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長胖的 杏裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 會運動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我們也永遠在一起 爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女每天都會做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如畫一般的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那是破滅的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父母已在五年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死於兇案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自活下來的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今依然做著這種夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法觸及的幸福家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走她雙親的慘劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這一帶的首起斬人魔事件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在準備體育節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她認為自己是個卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然教師的企圖顯而易見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她卻不反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封閉心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著風平浪靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好又會被斬人魔盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人不安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來性騷擾麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}這可不行啊老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女認識到自己寄生在他們身上活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}正臣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}園原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 不爭氣的登場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 等了很久？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等太久差點都成化石了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？根號3分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根號？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根號是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少噴個負20分啥的容易理解嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已躺在醫院的病床上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜養一段時間就會好轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要住院一周左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}之後要去辦一下手續哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了部分記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我沒有這種閒工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}等等 贄川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「盯住她」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我內心的聲音這麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5號室的贄川先生還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊 希望他的傷口別裂開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他宰了他宰了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄 你的心意我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也不用勉強陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的個人問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵斬人魔今晚也不一定出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不原諒斬人魔那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它是妖刀還是什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刀的話折斷就死了吧 不死我也要宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是和他們糾纏的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事麼？西瓜蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在跟那邊的蟑螂打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 眼神可以殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如詛咒 眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這種東西殺死的可能性有0.0000000000000000675%左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒保喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒…酒保？該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你用眼神瞪了人 那死在我手下也沒得怨言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贄川春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師的那個反應到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經11點了啊 學生快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起 馬上回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？附近的話我們送你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人報110東池袋中央公園發生數名青少年鬥毆事件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即前往 請講
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先生 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要送的話在派出所等等 待會兒送你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不認為從頭到尾把「瞬間」換成「剎那」的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是篇美文了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說 其實還是不想走尋常路對吧 游馬卿也到這年紀了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不再認為只要否定世上正常大人們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會受叛逆期的中學生歡迎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批判思想批判社會就是個性也太膚淺了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游馬崎會說書不好 真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游馬卿以前自費出版的小說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然輪不到我這個睡覺的人發話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴被砍了 認真收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 這次和卡茲塔諾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不認識的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們是達拉斯的成員…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點為他人哭泣的感性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到悲傷卻自閉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為斬人魔不可原諒卻自閉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 我們為什麼加入達拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想過平淡無奇的日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在外國認個綠頭髮的可愛女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回國後住在美女三姐妹隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過著溫馨快樂的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種平凡的日常生活就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《四葉妹妹！》《四葉妹妹！》？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說斬人魔是在這附近出現的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種孩子會被襲擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那人眼睛血紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一塊小心病復發了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡草
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞飛他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪 塞爾堤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 門田太殘忍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家剛說想過太平日子就幹這票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時只有這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說都算正當防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無頭騎士和…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田田看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是平和島靜雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你哦 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}好想見你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常非常愛你哦 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要採訪…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是寫成這份報道 一切都會順利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子會回到我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女兒的彆扭關係也會改善
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和從前一樣…一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.83,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}こんな時代には夢があるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.83,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}如今這時代還有何夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:03.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}そんな口グセは言い飽きたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:03.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}這樣的口頭禪早已說膩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:07.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}ずっと惡ぶってきたつもりだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:07.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}雖然一直裝作不良
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:10.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}最近それさえも虛しくなるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:10.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}最近連這也變得空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:14.03,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an1}「會いたい」とか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:14.03,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}什麼好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:18.96,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}良く似た街に空回る雜音のフレーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:18.96,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}如出一轍的城市裡雜音般的空談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}そんなもので騙されない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}這種話騙不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.80,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}自分の想いなら判ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}自己的想法我自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}僕らは自由だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}我們是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:33.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}葉わぬ夢なんて　無いと何處か願うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:33.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}心中隱隱祈禱著所有夢想都會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:34.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}誰もがそうやって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:34.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}所有人都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:41.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}自分探してるんだ　走り續けて見えたものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:41.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}找尋著自我 不斷往前衝
